{"tid":2249727,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"Paws United Charity利用貓狗籌款 頻頻走失狗隻","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T09:31:36.000Z","uid":253247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6254f4be3f388ffb619b0240a8d8482200b816a3","tid":2249727,"uid":253247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"之前已經聽過唔少人講le間機構既惡行<br />\n包括頻頻利用幫狗隻籌醫藥費黎籌款，最後好多錢用哂黎請明星promote自己同賣地鐵廣告，從來冇disclose過有關帳目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPaws United Charity喺三日內已經有兩隻狗走失左<br />\n綜合Facebook唔少資訊顯示<br />\n<strong>1.機構從來無家訪暫托家庭<br />\n基本上只要你有手有腳就可以拎走隻狗<br />\n完全無關心暫養人是否有足夠能力睇實隻狗<br />\n2.機構未回應會唔會參與搜救工作<br />\n3.曾經有暫托人暫托左一隻因為太瘦而突然胃反轉要做手術既狗仔<br />\n暫養人事前對病情毫不知情 該機構亦選擇隱瞞<br />\n後來更表示暫養人需要全數支付狗隻做手術既手術費</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">咁請問你地咁大間charity機構點解從來無擺錢落去做狗隻既醫藥費？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而昨日走失咗嘅兩歲Husky Alec<br />\n機構前幾日先喺Facebook籌款$80000<br />\n表示隻狗有抽搐情況每月需要$10000醫藥費<br />\n而前暫托人們表示機構係無幫輕過暫托人<br />\n亦有人喺Facebook表示「如果隻狗無暫托肯再暫嘅，貴機構就等佢再發癲咬人咬9...就會拎去漁農啪」<br />\n狗仔就喺昨日在塘福走失<br />\n對於會否參與搜救工作全無回應<br />\nInbox幾多次都係已讀不回<br />\n有帶tracker都搵唔返, 想問個tracker係用黎托柒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9sFgap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9sFgap.jpg&h=e62a6ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望住附近既朋友可以幫手搵下隻狗仔之餘<br />\n亦都關注下所謂charity既呃錢同管理不善既問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/154292385155728/posts/752701775314783/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F154292385155728%2Fposts%2F752701775314783%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZrsYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=ad102273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/154292385155728/posts/752701775314783/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"e111b1010fe74ac77c8e0e1ad5011bab7a8522e1","tid":2249727,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ee4e16f8c6955b8f81515d9f7a13c0d4c2888a","tid":2249727,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"狗要家訪？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未養過狗"},{"pid":"18c3ab8baa908dea582cd3355b60abe07d28c36d","tid":2249727,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"Btw charity嘅話係咪好似東華三院嗰啲咁， 唔會自己拎條數po上網， 政府監察等"},{"pid":"ccdd80a67e149971a9df66ce981fc2367b71f89d","tid":2249727,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"雪橇講明頸圈有追蹤器<br />\n咁都搵唔返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bd6a359e18ac348ccd5b4f514baae98813a406","tid":2249727,"uid":360231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccdd80a67e149971a9df66ce981fc2367b71f89d","tid":2249727,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"雪橇講明頸圈有追蹤器<br />\n咁都搵唔返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"問左現任暫托人，佢話個追蹤器係新買既，佢可能唔識搞，所以其實個追蹤器唔work。佢話諗住第二日問舖頭啲人點搞，但嗰日Alec就走失左"}]}